The complete **FishHunt** application is now built and launching. Here's a summary of everything implemented:

## 🎣 What's Built

### Core Features
- **Authentication** — Register, login, logout, password reset with Laravel Breeze (Blade)
- **Roles & Permissions** — Database-backed Admin/Moderator/Member roles with granular permissions and admin UI
- **Catch Posts** — Upload 1-5 photos, track species/bait/gear/weight/length, location with privacy controls
- **Public Feed** — Filterable by species, location, date range with card-based layout
- **Likes & Comments** — Real-time like toggling via AJAX, threaded comments
- **Reports & Moderation** — Report posts/comments, moderator review panel with dismiss/hide/delete actions

### Hunt Planner (The Impressive Feature)
- **Smart Briefings** — Weather forecast, tide times (coastal), species recommendations, bait & tackle suggestions, timing tips
- **Interactive Checklist** — Auto-generated, categorized, with satisfying tick animations and progress bar
- **Shareable Links** — Read-only public view for sharing with mates
- **Provider Abstraction** — `WeatherProviderInterface`, `TideProviderInterface`, `SpeciesInfoProviderInterface` with demo mode fallback

### Polish
- **Badges** — 10 achievement badges (First Catch, Species Explorer, Popular Catch, etc.)
- **Profile Pages** — Stats, badges, recent catches & hunts
- **Mobile-first** — Fully responsive dark theme with glassmorphism, gradients, and micro-animations
- **Map Embeds** — OpenStreetMap for location previews

### Demo Accounts
| Role | Email | Password |
|------|-------|----------|
| Admin | `admin@fishhunt.app` | `password` |
| Moderator | `mod@fishhunt.app` | `password` |
| Member | `member@fishhunt.app` | `password` |

